<p><b>Gerhard Richter</b> (born <span class="mw-formatted-date" title="1932-02-09"><span class="mw-formatted-date" title="02-09"><a href="/wiki/February_9" title="February 9">February 9</a></span>, <a href="/wiki/1932" title="1932">1932</a></span>) is a <a href="/wiki/Germany" title="Germany">German</a> <a href="/wiki/Artist" title="Artist">artist</a>.</p>
<table id="toc" class="toc" summary="Contents">
